6c1b7f1c03a0d522aaa86bf22753a897316d488ea5226df6f87f9c53b5345e2f3f61b97b4d4754aa5c1ea9b05e411bbf65bdd72dfcd9e90b179c1941abd1a8ac  0001-Allow-changing-of-CONFIG_PATH-during-compile-time.patch"
